OL,6,FIt is the most difficult time in
OL,7,FUkraine in months, ITV News
OL,8,FCorrespondent John Ray reports
OL,10,FCrossing western border is always a
OL,11,Fdisorientating experience.
OL,13,FToday, the sun shines and the traffic
OL,14,Fflows swiftly on the highway to Kyiv.
OL,16,FIt can be hard to keep in mind this
OL,17,Fnation has been fighting for its
OL,18,Fexistence for two grinding years.
