OL,6,FBut away to the east, where we are
OL,7,Fheading, that war has reached another
OL,8,Fimportant juncture.
OL,10,FThere, troops have mounted a series of
OL,11,Fincursions - the most sustained since
OL,12,F2022. Around 8,000 civilians have been
OL,13,Fevacuated from the path of their
OL,14,Fattack.
OL,16,FUkrainian commanders, mindful that
OL,17,FMoscow may be mounting a feint, have
OL,18,Fstill had to deploy reserves to the
OL,19,FKharkiv region.
