OL,6,FThe US secretary of state is in Kyiv
OL,7,Ftoday to stand symbolically shoulder-
OL,8,Fto-shoulder with his embattled hosts.
OL,10,FHe comes with the promise of $2
OL,11,Fbillion (#1.6 billion) of military aid
OL,12,F- and for the first time gave Ukraine
OL,13,Flicence to deploy western weapons
OL,14,Fagainst targets inside Russia itself.
OL,16,FIn the past there was reluctance to do
OL,17,Fso for fear of escalation.
OL,19,FPerhaps the public change of heart is
OL,20,Fa measure of the sudden seriousness of
OL,21,Fthe situation.
