OL,6,FSo too is Ukraine President Volodymyr
OL,7,FZelenskyy's decision to cancel all
OL,8,Fforeign engagements for the time being.
OL,10,F"It's a very serious situation," a
OL,11,FUkrainian friend tells me. "We still
OL,12,Fdon't have the artillery or the
OL,13,Fmissiles."
OL,15,FThe US military aid was delayed for
OL,16,Fmonths, so this was a crisis made in
OL,17,Fpart by political infighting in
OL,18,FWashington.
